### MDC Format Guidelines
- Use proper heading hierarchy
- Include code blocks with language specification
- Add metadata sections where applicable
- Include visual references (screenshots, diagrams)
- Document all design tokens (colors, spacing, typography)
- Provide code examples for reusable patterns

