## Implementation Notes

### Handling Protected Sites
When encountering Cloudflare or similar protections:
1. Use browser automation (Puppeteer/Playwright)
2. Wait for JavaScript execution
3. Handle challenge pages
4. Maintain session cookies
5. Respect rate limits

### Best Practices
- Document assumptions when direct access isn't possible
- Include screenshots for visual reference
- Version control all analysis files
- Update analysis when site changes
- Maintain privacy and security considerations

